OL,6,FAll this on a day with a programme
OL,7,Fstart which was absolutely not up for
OL,8,Fnegotiation ` the Eurovision Song
OL,9,FContest, of course, begins at
OL,10,Fprecisely 8pm UK time. Indeed until
OL,11,Fthe 80s it was probably the only light
OL,12,Fentertainment show to be introduced
OL,13,Fover the clock.
OL,15,FStuck between the two live events was
OL,16,FDoctor Who. This episode ` The
OL,17,FInterstellar Song Contest ` was
OL,18,Fobviously planned with the day in mind.
