OL,6,FBut any overrun to the FA Cup would
OL,7,Fhave pushed the Time Lord over to BBC
OL,8,FTwo ` the last thing the programme
OL,9,Fneeded.
OL,11,FAll in all, it was the kind of day
OL,12,Fwhere schedulers and Presentation have
OL,13,Fto anticipate a whole range of
OL,14,Foptions. Undoubtedly consideration had
OL,15,Fto be given to a hypothetical
OL,16,Fsituation where the kickoff had to be
OL,17,Fdelayed too. Imagine if the match was
OL,18,Fstill in progress as events were
OL,19,Fgetting underway in Basel?
