OL,4,CITV 1 on Saturday
OL,6,FThe only solution for the regional
OL,7,Fnews was to push it to a mid-afternoon
OL,8,Fslot. It might have meant tighter
OL,9,Fdeadlines for journalists but there
OL,10,Fwere no realistic alternatives `
OL,11,FScotland and the English regions
OL,12,Fcannot opt on BBC Two.
OL,14,FHowever ITV 1 ` without the wider
OL,15,Fcomplexities of the BBC schedule to
OL,16,Fconsider ` simply dropped their
OL,17,Fregional bulletin altogether.
OL,19,FITV 1 could have scheduled the
OL,20,Fbulletin for lunchtime or put it in a
OL,21,Fmid evening slot.
