OL,6,FDid they even consider this?
OL,8,FFor the second time in a month, ITV 1
OL,9,Fdid not schedule a regional news
OL,10,Fbulletin for reasons of expediency.
OL,12,FI go back to the point I made a few
OL,13,Fweeks ago.
OL,15,FThere is no suggestion that ITV is in
OL,16,Fbreach of licence requirements but the
OL,17,Fregional news is a key part of its PSB
OL,18,Frequirement.
