OL,6,FIf there is no demand for weekend
OL,7,Fbulletins ` a questionable contention
OL,8,F` ITV should have the courage to say
OL,9,Fthis, drop them officially and put its
OL,10,Fresources into enhancing weekday
OL,11,Fprovision.
OL,13,FThe spirit of regulatory requirements
OL,14,Fsurely matters as much as the letter
OL,15,Fof them.
